INSTALLATION
    Wendy can be easily compiled and installed. See file "INSTALL" for
    instructions.
    
    Wendy uses a lot of generated code. If you want to make changes to the
    source code, you might need the following tools to regenerate the code:
     * Flex (http://flex.sourceforge.net)
     * Bison (http://www.gnu.org/software/bison)
     * Gengetopt (http://www.gnu.org/software/gengetopt)


DOCUMENTATION
    The directory "doc" contains a documentation of Wendy. It can also be
    downloaded at <http://service-technology.org/files/wendy/wendy.pdf>.
